{"tid":1476174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本10歲女孩來港機場訪示威者　「想了解真相就與當事人對話」","createTime":"2019-08-15T17:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T03:42:29.000Z","uid":60281,"like":85,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0c04cef7601c751126fc50d8dffa94c7ff787196","tid":1476174,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3162301/org/9c4b898dbbc9317f9a2a233b6c1e8f8b.jpg/TjXG6w_wZmImH_QqNv5HKEYho40XT4takWQZ8JFkGfA?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3162301%2Forg%2F9c4b898dbbc9317f9a2a233b6c1e8f8b.jpg%2FTjXG6w_wZmImH_QqNv5HKEYho40XT4takWQZ8JFkGfA%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=7bf1d83b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因反對逃犯條例爭議持續，自星期一起，示威者接連於機場進行集會示威，引起國際高度關注。<br />\n<br />\n日本有一位10歲小女孩在爸爸的陪同下，昨天專程從日本來港，訪問於機場靜坐的示威者，瞬間成為全國熱話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3161827/org/99208932d80151e3adf8656591090349.jpg/Fj7FxR58H8AzDxzzGcZaGcDzPraqAdQnj4ZJ4Y-GSeE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3161827%2Forg%2F99208932d80151e3adf8656591090349.jpg%2FFj7FxR58H8AzDxzzGcZaGcDzPraqAdQnj4ZJ4Y-GSeE&h=5b485969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟爸爸專程來港訪問示威者<br />\n<br />\n據日本WBS新聞（ワールドビジネスサテライト）報道，日本一名小學4年級生 島津知佳小朋友（10歲）昨日在爸爸陪同下，從日本專程到香港國際機場訪問示威者。<br />\n<br />\n島津知佳表示自己從新聞得知香港的示威運動，但未清楚掌握運動背景，便來香港作自由研究。她認為要了解事實真相，必須與當事人進行實際對話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成為全國熱話<br />\n<br />\n該段新聞一出，知佳即成為全國焦點，至少有3則相關帖文登上Twitter熱門。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛大讚知佳對追求真相的執著，笑言她是「真記者」；同時亦盛讚爸爸的無條件支持，表示這是很難得的家庭教育及體驗。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民亦對日本主流媒體感到失望，狠批他們的報道充斥著各種偏頗及隱瞞，實在「連小孩也比不上」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3162256/org/eb8a3ded53d25144bb8084d8e936898d.png/V4AXifVUPA1L4NReK374xznF92ZHa0E1plkVsaZZFbE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3162256%2Forg%2Feb8a3ded53d25144bb8084d8e936898d.png%2FV4AXifVUPA1L4NReK374xznF92ZHa0E1plkVsaZZFbE&h=26d0bbae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3162053/org/dc5fbb7485a4d5473a3c42515a8fe400.jpg/szVemzVloYIPzJgNTUwcIgsa-QAGqKiOUpUfUVKVH1E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3162053%2Forg%2Fdc5fbb7485a4d5473a3c42515a8fe400.jpg%2FszVemzVloYIPzJgNTUwcIgsa-QAGqKiOUpUfUVKVH1E&h=20802785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3162054/org/33a14be64fb7a3ffeac882fa52f7a6e8.jpg/fhqYXW5NLYQjJ4qOys14tK1Jyl2bFLSmxoISMMaCEjA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3162054%2Forg%2F33a14be64fb7a3ffeac882fa52f7a6e8.jpg%2FfhqYXW5NLYQjJ4qOys14tK1Jyl2bFLSmxoISMMaCEjA&h=4d9a178b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3162060/org/8e150a22cdda826ffe8403ff409089b9.jpg/nhdw5OyJ65sE4twPnNZZuJJGe9MESr1HaO7qxWju6sU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3162060%2Forg%2F8e150a22cdda826ffe8403ff409089b9.jpg%2Fnhdw5OyJ65sE4twPnNZZuJJGe9MESr1HaO7qxWju6sU&h=83d230e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%96%8B%E7%BD%90/364013/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC10%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E8%A8%AA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E6%83%B3%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8%E5%B0%B1%E8%88%87%E7%95%B6%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25BD%2590%2F364013%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC10%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25A9%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E7%